  {
    "slug": "6-days-vietnam-highlights-tour-da-nang-hoi-an-hanoi-halong-bay",
    "title": "6 Days Vietnam Highlights Tour \u2013 Da Nang, Hoi An, Hanoi & Halong Bay",
    "description": "Experience the best of Vietnam with this 6 Days Vietnam Highlights Tour, covering the country\u2019s most iconic destinations including Da Nang, Ba Na Hills, Hoi An, Hanoi, and Halong Bay. This well-crafted itinerary offers a perfect balance of culture, nature, history, and relaxation.\n\nBegin your journey in Da Nang, exploring stunning coastal landscapes, Marble Mountains, and the famous Golden Bridge at Ba Na Hills. Discover the charm of Hoi An Ancient Town, enjoy a lantern boat ride, and experience local life at the Coconut Village. Fly to Hanoi to explore historical landmarks, bustling old quarters, and vibrant street culture.\n\nThe tour concludes with a scenic Halong Bay day cruise, where you\u2019ll sail through dramatic limestone formations and visit breathtaking caves. Designed for couples, families, and first-time visitors, this Vietnam tour package ensures comfort, guided experiences, and unforgettable memories from start to finish.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "6 days",
    "group_size": "8-12",
    "best_time": "January, February, March, April, November, December",
