  {
    "slug": "6-nights-7-days-kathmandu-pokhara-nagarkot",
    "title": "6 Nights 7 days Kathmandu- Pokhara-Nagarkot",
    "description": "Experience Nepal\u2019s cultural heritage and natural beauty on this 6 Nights / 7 Days Kathmandu \u2013 Pokhara \u2013 Nagarkot Tour. Discover ancient temples and UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Kathmandu, enjoy breathtaking Himalayan views and lakeside relaxation in Pokhara, and unwind in Nagarkot, famous for its stunning sunrise and panoramic mountain vistas. A perfect blend of culture, nature, and serenity, ideal for couples, families, and leisure travelers.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "7 days",
    "group_size": "2-8 people",
    "best_time": "",
    "image": "/uploads/tours/6-nights-7-days-kathmandu-pokhara-nagarkot/tour_1766900195833.jpg",
    "gallery": [
      "/uploads/tours/6-nights-7-days-kathmandu-pokhara-nagarkot/tour_1766900460234.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/6-nights-7-days-kathmandu-pokhara-nagarkot/tour_1766900460251.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/6-nights-7-days-kathmandu-pokhara-nagarkot/tour_1766900460264.jpg"
    ],
    "highlights": [
      "Explore UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Kathmandu, including ancient temples and historic squares",
      "Enjoy spectacular Himalayan views and serene boating at Phewa Lake, Pokhara",
      "Witness a breathtaking sunrise over the Himalayas from Nagarkot",
      "Experience the natural beauty of Pokhara Valley with mountain and lake scenery",
      "Visit famous cultural landmarks such as Swayambhunath and Pashupatinath",
      "Comfortable accommodations with scenic drives across Nepal\u2019s countryside"
    ],
    "inclusions": [
      "Traditional Welcome drink on arrival (Nonalcoholic)",
      "03 Nights\u2019 accommodation at Kathmandu Hotel",
      "02 Nights\u2019 accommodation at Pokhara Hotel",
      "01 Nights\u2019 accommodation at Nagarkot Hotel",
      "1-liter mineral water per day",
      "Sunrise tour at Pokhara Pumdikot Shiva Temple.",
      "Arrival and departure transfer with assistance by A/C Vehicle",
      "All sightseeing and excursions as mentioned in the itinerary",
      "All transfers & sightseeing by private air condition vehicle",
      "Round trip transportation for Kathmandu- Nagarkot by Private vehicle",
      "Vehicles are not to be disposal and are available as per itinerary only",
      "All current Nepal Government taxes"
    ],
