  {
    "slug": "discover-chinas-spirit-in-beijing-shanghai",
    "title": "Discover China\u2019s Spirit in Beijing & Shanghai",
    "description": "Discover the dynamic spirit of China with an unforgettable journey through Beijing, Shanghai, and Chengdu. From Beijing\u2019s majestic imperial landmarks and rich cultural heritage to Shanghai\u2019s dazzling skyline and modern cosmopolitan energy, and finally to Chengdu\u2019s laid-back charm and world-famous giant pandas, this tour blends history, innovation, and natural beauty. Experience the essence of China\u2014 past, present, and future\u2014across three of its most captivating cities.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "6 days",
    "group_size": "2-8",
    "best_time": "",
    "image": "/uploads/tours/discover-chinas-spirit-in-beijing-shanghai/tour_1766465732623.jpg",
    "gallery": [
      "/uploads/tours/discover-chinas-spirit-in-beijing-shanghai/tour_1766465741121.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/discover-chinas-spirit-in-beijing-shanghai/tour_1766465741239.webp",
      "/uploads/tours/discover-chinas-spirit-in-beijing-shanghai/tour_1766465741407.avif"
    ],
    "highlights": [
      "Explore historic Beijing: Tiananmen Square, Forbidden City & Temple of Heaven",
      "Walk on the Great Wall of China at Juyong Pass",
      "Photo stop at the Bird\u2019s Nest Stadium",
      "Travel by high-speed bullet train to Shanghai",
      "Discover Shanghai\u2019s top sights: Jade Buddha Temple, Yu Garden, The Bund",
      "Enjoy shopping & nightlife at Xintiandi and Nanjing Road"
    ],
