        "description": "Arrive at Dubai International Airport and receive a warm welcome from our representative. Transfer to your hotel and relax. In the evening, enjoy a memorable Dhow Cruise Dinner along Dubai Creek aboard a beautifully decorated traditional dhow. Savor a lavish buffet dinner with refreshments while admiring Dubai\u2019s glittering skyline at night. Overnight stay in Dubai.\n",
