        "title": "Half-Day Dubai City Tour & Burj Khalifa 124th Floor (Non-Prime Time)",
        "description": "After breakfast, embark on a guided half-day city tour showcasing Dubai\u2019s iconic attractions. Visit the Dubai Museum and Jumeirah Mosque, and enjoy photo stops at the famous Burj Al Arab and Atlantis The Palm (outside view). Continue to Dubai Mall, followed by the highlight of the day\u2014ascending the Burj Khalifa\u2019s 124th Floor (Non-Prime Time) for breathtaking panoramic views. Return to the hotel for overnight stay.\n\n",
