  {
    "slug": "ghandruk-tour-4n-5d",
    "title": "Ghandruk Tour 4N 5D",
    "description": "This 5-day Pokhara and Ghandruk tour offers a perfect mix of scenic flights, Himalayan trekking, cultural village life, and spiritual sightseeing. Enjoy the beauty of Phewa Lake in Pokhara, trek through charming mountain villages to Ghandruk with stunning Annapurna views, and explore Nepal\u2019s iconic heritage sites in Kathmandu, including Swayambhunath and Pashupatinath. Ideal for a short yet enriching Himalayan experience.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "5 days",
    "group_size": "2-8",
    "best_time": "",
    "image": "/uploads/tours/ghandruk-tour-4n-5d/tour_1766568139456.jpg",
    "gallery": [
