      "All Sightseeing and excursions as mentioned in the itinerary.",
      "All transfer & Sightseeing by private Air condition Vehicle",
      "Round trip transportation for Gorakhpur \u2013 Pokhara \u2013 Kathmandu \u2013 Chitwan \u2013 Gorakhpur",
      "Vehicle are not to be at disposal and are available as per itinerary only (point- point basis)",
