      "risks_liability": "All tours in Tibet are conducted under Tibet Tourism Bureau (TTB) rules and regulations. Company shall not be responsible for changes due to unavoidable circumstances such as landslide, road blockage, flood, snow, political unrest, flight cancellation, delays, sickness or accidents. Extra costs shall be borne by clients."
