        "description": "After breakfast, visit Boudhanath Stupa (world heritage site) & Jala Narayan Temple (Sleeping Vishnu) fly to Pokhara. Arrival in Pokhara transfer to Hotel. Overnight at a hotel in Pokhara.\n\n",
