    "slug": "kathmandupokharachitwan-tour-package-",
    "title": "Kathmandu\u2013Pokhara\u2013Chitwan Tour Package ",
    "description": "Discover the best of Nepal on this 5 Nights / 6 Days Kathmandu \u2013 Pokhara \u2013 Chitwan Tour. Explore Kathmandu\u2019s UNESCO heritage sites, enjoy stunning Himalayan views and lakeside serenity in Pokhara, and experience thrilling jungle safaris and rich Tharu culture in Chitwan. A perfect blend of culture, nature, and adventure, ideal for families, couples, and first-time visitors.",
