  {
    "slug": "langtang-gosaikunda-lake-trek-7-days-sacred-himalayan-journey",
    "title": "Langtang Gosaikunda Lake Trek \u2013 7 Days Sacred Himalayan Journey",
    "description": "The Langtang Gosaikunda Lake Trek is a perfect blend of spiritual significance, alpine adventure, and raw Himalayan beauty. This 7-day journey takes you from the vibrant streets of Kathmandu to the sacred high-altitude lakes of Gosaikunda (4,380m), revered by both Hindus and Buddhists.\n\nStarting with a scenic drive to Dhunche, the trek gradually ascends through lush pine forests, Tamang villages, cascading waterfalls, and dramatic mountain landscapes. Along the trail, you\u2019ll experience the warm hospitality of local communities, explore ancient monasteries like Sing Gompa (Chandanbari), and witness breathtaking views of Langtang Lirung, Ganesh Himal, Manaslu, and surrounding peaks.\n\nThe highlight of the trek is the arrival at Gosaikunda Lake, a sacred alpine lake believed to have been created by Lord Shiva. Surrounded by rugged Himalayan terrain and serene glacial waters, the area offers a deeply peaceful and spiritual experience. The return journey follows the same scenic route back to Dhunche before driving to Kathmandu, leaving you with unforgettable memories of Nepal\u2019s natural and cultural richness.\n\nThis trek is ideal for adventure seekers, spiritual travelers, and nature lovers looking for a moderate Himalayan trek with deep cultural meaning.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "7 days",
    "group_size": "6-10",
    "best_time": "March, April, May, September, October, November",
    "image": "/uploads/tours/langtang-gosaikunda-lake-trek-7-days-sacred-himalayan-journey/tour_1769941793905.jpg",
    "gallery": [
      "/uploads/tours/langtang-gosaikunda-lake-trek-7-days-sacred-himalayan-journey/tour_1769942875033.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/langtang-gosaikunda-lake-trek-7-days-sacred-himalayan-journey/tour_1769942875040.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/langtang-gosaikunda-lake-trek-7-days-sacred-himalayan-journey/tour_1769942875066.jpg"
    ],
    "highlights": [
      "Visit the sacred alpine lakes of Gosaikunda (4,380m), revered by Hindus and Buddhists",
      "Scenic drive through the Trishuli River valley and traditional hill villages",
      "Trek through pine, rhododendron, and alpine forests",
      "Experience Tamang culture and Tibetan-influenced mountain lifestyle",
      "Explore Sing Gompa (Chandanbari Monastery) and famous yak cheese factory",
      "Comfortable stays in teahouses and a 3-star hotel in Kathmandu",
      "Moderate trek suitable for both adventure seekers and spiritual travelers"
    ],
    "inclusions": [
      "Airport pickup and drop-off by private vehicle",
