  {
    "slug": "nepal-tour-3-nights-4-days",
    "title": "Nepal Tour 3 Nights 4 Days",
    "description": "This 4-day journey offers a serene and enriching exploration of Kathmandu\u2019s spiritual heart and cultural treasures. Beginning with a warm welcome in the capital, the tour sets a devotional tone with an evening aarti at the sacred Pashupatinath Temple. Over the next days, travelers uncover the essence of the Kathmandu Valley through visits to revered UNESCO World Heritage Sites, including Swayambhunath Stupa, Boudhanath Stupa, Kathmandu Durbar Square, and the holy Jal Narayan (Sleeping Vishnu) Temple.\n\nThe experience is enhanced by a scenic cable car ride to Chandragiri Hills, where panoramic valley views and a visit to Baleshwar Mahadev Temple provide moments of peace and reflection. A cultural visit to Patan Durbar Square showcases the artistic brilliance of Newari civilization. Designed for those seeking spirituality, heritage, and gentle exploration, this tour delivers a meaningful and memorable Kathmandu escape.\n",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "4 days",
    "group_size": "2-8",
