      {
        "day": 1,
        "title": "Arrive in Kathmandu",
        "description": "Arrive at Tribhuvan International Airport and transfer to your hotel. In the evening, visit the famous Pashupatinath temple to attend the beautiful evening aarti on the banks of the Bagmati River. Overnight stay in Kathmandu.",
        "accommodation": "3-Star Hotel",
        "meals": "N/A"
      },
      {
        "day": 2,
        "title": "Kathmandu-Drive to Bhaktapur-Doleshwar-Saga",
        "description": "After breakfast, drive to Bhaktapur, Known for its medieval charm and Bhaktapur Durbar Square. Continue to Doleshwar Temple, a historic Shiva temple, and then to Sanga, home to Kailashnath Mahadev Statue, one of the tallest Shiva statues in the world. Return to Kathmandu in the evening. Overnight stay in Kathmandu.",
        "accommodation": "3-Star Hotel",
        "meals": "Breakfast"
      },
      {
        "day": 3,
        "title": "Kathmandu Half day Sightseeing-Drive to Nagarkot",
        "description": "After breakfast, enjoy half day sightseeing in Kathmandu, visit Swoyambhunath (Monkey Temple), Kathmandu Durbar Square (Living God Kumari). Drive to Nagarkot, a hills station famous for panoramic views of the Himalayans. Enjoy the evening watching the sunset over the mountains. Overnight stay in Nagarkot.",
        "accommodation": "3-Star Hotel",
        "meals": "Breakfast"
      },
      {
