    "slug": "thailand-island-city-experience-8-days-of-wonder",
    "title": "Thailand Island & City Experience \u2013 8 Days of Wonder",
    "description": "Discover the best of Thailand with a perfectly balanced journey through vibrant cities and tropical islands. Begin in Bangkok, exploring its lively atmosphere and iconic attractions before flying to Phuket, Thailand\u2019s famous beach paradise. Enjoy a full-day Phi Phi Island tour with crystal-clear waters, stunning limestone cliffs, and unforgettable island scenery. Continue to Krabi for an exciting Four Island tour, featuring beautiful beaches and snorkeling spots. Return to Bangkok for a memorable evening dinner cruise and a fun-filled visit to Safari World and Marine Park. This tour offers the ideal mix of relaxation, adventure, and cultural experiences.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "8 days",
    "group_size": "2-8",
