  {
    "slug": "ultimate-10-day-east-asia-combo-thailand-malaysia-singapore-expedition",
    "title": "Ultimate 10-Day East Asia Combo: Thailand, Malaysia & Singapore Expedition",
    "description": "Experience the best of East Asia in one seamless 9-night, 10-day journey. This curated combo package takes you through the dazzling highlights of Thailand, Malaysia, and Singapore, combining modern cityscapes with tropical island escapes. \n\nYour adventure begins in Thailand, where you'll explore the vibrant streets of Bangkok and the sun-drenched beaches of Pattaya. Enjoy a high-speed excursion to Coral Island for water sports and paragliding before diving into Bangkok\u2019s rich history with a tour of its famous Wats (temples). \n\nNext, fly to Singapore, the \"Heart of Asia.\" Discover the iconic Merlion Park, take a cable car to Sentosa Island, and witness the spectacular Wings of Time show. \n\nThe journey concludes in Malaysia, featuring the ultra-modern Petronas Twin Towers in Kuala Lumpur and the breezy heights of Genting Highlands. Experience the cultural depth of the Batu Caves and the ancient Indo-Moorish architecture of the capital city.",
    "price": 0,
    "duration": "10 days",
    "group_size": "10",
    "best_time": "January, February, March, November, December",
    "image": "",
    "gallery": [
      "/uploads/tours/ultimate-10-day-east-asia-combo-thailand-malaysia-singapore-expedition/tour_1769509785722.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/ultimate-10-day-east-asia-combo-thailand-malaysia-singapore-expedition/tour_1769509912008.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/ultimate-10-day-east-asia-combo-thailand-malaysia-singapore-expedition/tour_1769509961354.jpg",
      "/uploads/tours/ultimate-10-day-east-asia-combo-thailand-malaysia-singapore-expedition/tour_1769510026278.jpg"
    ],
    "highlights": [
      "Thailand: Coral Island speed boat tour, Bangkok city & temple exploration",
      "Singapore: Sentosa Island, Madame Tussauds, and Marina Bay sights",
      "Malaysia: Genting Highland cable car ride and Kuala Lumpur landmarks",
      "Comfort: Stay in handpicked 3-star accommodations throughout the trip"
    ],
    "inclusions": [
